tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE fuel_efficiency_data (
  vehicle_id INT,
  manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
  model VARCHAR(255),
  fuel_type VARCHAR(50),
  fuel_economy FLOAT,
  engine_size FLOAT,
  transmission VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
  vehicle_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  make VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  model VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  year INT NOT NULL,
  fuel_type VARCHAR(30) NOT NULL,
  mileage INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE fuel_efficiency (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id INT REFERENCES vehicles(vehicle_id),
  date DATE NOT NULL,
  fuel_consumed FLOAT NOT NULL,
  distance_traveled FLOAT NOT NULL,
  efficiency FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_make VARCHAR(50),
    vehicle_model VARCHAR(50),
    fuel_type VARCHAR(20),
    fuel_efficiency FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE fuel_consumption (
    consumption_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    trip_id INT,
    fuel_used FLOAT,
    distance_traveled FLOAT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_vehicle_id FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES vehicles(vehicle_id)
);

CREATE TABLE trips (
    trip_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    trip_date DATE,
    trip_distance FLOAT,
    trip_duration INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_vehicle_id FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES vehicles(vehicle_id)
);

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
  vehicle_id INT,
  vehicle_name VARCHAR(50),
  fuel_type VARCHAR(20),
  fuel_capacity FLOAT,
  mileage FLOAT,
  PRIMARY KEY (vehicle_id)
)

CREATE TABLE trips (
  trip_id INT,
  vehicle_id INT,
  trip_date DATE,
  distance_traveled FLOAT,
  fuel_consumed FLOAT,
  PRIMARY KEY (trip_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES vehicles(vehicle_id)
)

CREATE TABLE fuel_types (
  fuel_type_id INT,
  fuel_name VARCHAR(20),
  fuel_density FLOAT,
  PRIMARY KEY (fuel_type_id)
)

CREATE TABLE fuel_prices (
  fuel_type_id INT,
  price_per_gallon FLOAT,
  price_date DATE,
  PRIMARY KEY (fuel_type_id, price_date),
  FOREIGN KEY (fuel_type_id) REFERENCES fuel_types(fuel_type_id)
)

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    make VARCHAR(50),
    model VARCHAR(50),
    year INT,
    fuel_type VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE fuel_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    fuel_date DATE,
    mileage INT,
    fuel_volume FLOAT,
    fuel_cost FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE trips (
    trip_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    trip_date DATE,
    start_location VARCHAR(100),
    end_location VARCHAR(100),
    distance FLOAT,
    duration INT
)

CREATE TABLE fuel_mileage (
    fuel_mileage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    fuel_record_id INT,
    mileage FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE fuel_efficiency (
    fuel_efficiency_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    average_mileage FLOAT,
    average_fuel_cost FLOAT
)
